        "content": "<p>Should there be a similar lemma to <code>List.length_append</code> with the rest of the <code>String</code> lemmas? It's a pretty short proof too, so I'm not really sure why it's not in there already, for convenience's sake</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">@[</span><span class=\"n\">simp</span><span class=\"kd\">]</span> <span class=\"kd\">theorem</span> <span class=\"n\">length_append</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">s1</span> <span class=\"n\">s2</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">String</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">s1</span> <span class=\"bp\">++</span> <span class=\"n\">s2</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">length</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"n\">s1.length</span> <span class=\"bp\">+</span> <span class=\"n\">s2.length</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">simp</span> <span class=\"n\">only</span> <span class=\"o\">[</span><span class=\"n\">String.length</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">String.append</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">List.length_append</span><span class=\"o\">]</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
